4 times 3 is 12 times 5 is 60.

00:05:12.250 --> 00:05:16.190
144 minus 60 is 84.

00:05:16.190 --> 00:05:17.990
All of that over 6.

00:05:17.990 --> 00:05:23.430
So x could be equal to 12 plus
the square root of 84 over 6

00:05:23.430 --> 00:05:29.930
